1) 8 types of variables:
int
double
string
bool
array
NULL
resource
object

2) gettype($...); or var_dump($...) - to get info about type of variable

3) type's converting
settype($var, "string") - universal form
intval($var)/boolval($var) - exact form

4) type coversion
$var1 = (bool)$var2;

5) check the type functions
is_bool($var);

6) check existence
isset($var);

7) check empty
empty($var);

8) define constant or check
define("NAME_OF_VAR", "value", true);
defined($var);

9) remove the var;
unset($var);
